        <prov id="DLM1472405" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">26A</label>
          <heading>Notice of exemption or approval of certain procurement procedures</heading>
          <prov.body>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
              <para>
                <text>If the Agency grants itself an exemption under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM227502">section 26(a)</intref></citation> or approves a procurement procedure under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="DLM227500">section 25(1)</intref></citation> to meet its own procurement requirements, it must publish the details of its exemption or approval (as the case may be) and its reasons on its Internet site.</text>
