              <history-note id="DLM1848533"><amended-provision>Section 37(1)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 December 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM321835">section 16</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Management Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 97).</history-note>
              <history-note id="DLM1476591"><amended-provision>Section 37(1)(b)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 August 2008</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM1313464">section 30(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Land Transport Management Amendment Act 2008</amending-leg> (2008 No 47).</history-note>
